descriptionHtml:
There was no wallpaper menu replacer that i liked, so i decide to do one my self. It\'s about a very promising game, certain a \"Monnalisa\" of videogames. Sons of Rome.
The pic is on dds format so you have only to put in texture/interface/object
Don\'t worry if the pic apear a little wide, in main menu \"wear\" perfectely. Very epic, very Imperial.
-Napoleone V.
